thermal: Remove ARCH_KIRKWOOD dependency

mach-kirkwood has been removed, now that kirkwood lives in mach-mvebu.
Depend on MACH_KIRKWOOD, which will be set when kirkwood is built as
part of ARCH_MVEBU.

